t anatomical systems further strengthens the case for chiropteran monophyly.", "access_right": "open", "creators": [{"name": "Simmons, Nancy B.", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/43c6cfc3c2929ff101a1943cb7638100", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/3e5c90f29fa4fd6b85e5745a47ced2da26d74b505489fe0d2f53586b98b3b421", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/XJ2AABEX", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/XJ2AABEX", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/7893913c9f913ee13ff39cc22b729779!/b224164-226605", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "3103", "pages": "1-54", "title": "American Museum Novitates"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/43c6cfc3c2929ff101a1943cb7638100"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545:items:XJ2AABEX"}], "license": {"id": "cc-by-4.0"}, "communities": [{"id": "batlit"}, {"id": "biosyslit"}], "relations": {"version": [{"index": 0, "is_last": true, "parent": {"pid_type": "recid", "pid_value": "17260722"}}]}}, "title": "The Case for Chiropteran Monophyly", "links": {"self": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/17260723", "self_html": "https://zenodo.org/records/17260723", "preview_html": "https://zenodo.org/records/